      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what's the point of reaching out? everyone else has their own lives and seeing them just makes me realize how much i've lost. i feel like a ghost walking around. i'm just tired of the effort it takes to exist. it's like i'm just waiting for something to stop the noise in my head.",
